subject: Letter names
msgSnippet: In the present enviroment of no truly standard letter names for Quickscript I propose using the contractions from the Quickscript manual by Kingsley Read.
messageBody:
In the present enviroment of no truly "standard" letter names for
Quickscript I propose using the contractions from the Quickscript
manual by Kingsley Read. This does not cover all the letters but would
aid in learning the standard contractions.
